Wednesday, April 7, 1993

MERIT DOCKET

92-2506. Lindeman v. Yanke.

In Quo Warranto. On motion to dismiss, motion for stay, and motion for leave to intervene. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Resnick, J., dissents.
